text: Múrna may refer to the following: *Mourne (barony), a former barony in County Down, Northern Ireland, known as Múrna in Irish * The Múrna, spelt in Old Irish as Mughdorna, a people that gave their name to Mourne; see Mourne (barony)#The Múrna *Muirne, the mother of Fionn mac Cumhail in the Fenian Cycle of Irish mythology
title: Múrna
